Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:46.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0250,,#21 毀滅之路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:47.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:05.67,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}人革聯 天柱極市警察署
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生體數據對照後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認定為絹江·庫斯洛德小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請確認
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 姐姐 姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Veda的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:01:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 「天人」計劃的主干係統
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎 利馮茲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科納家族為了這一刻 已經等了200多年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.85,0:01:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲 經由Veda 調出擊退Trinity的部隊影像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.61,0:01:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能把我方的數據…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經屏蔽了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.01,0:01:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.21,0:01:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下載完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是擬太陽爐搭載型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.44,0:01:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭正在擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:50.15,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}非洲大陸 西北部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.42,0:01:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 還沒跟拉格納聯繫上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒呢 沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國都有了新型機 到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰哥 我們該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現已通過Level 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在進入Level 6的掌控作業
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了打發時間 請您看看這些情報吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 拉格納·哈維已完成GN-X的配置了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 他的使命也就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:39.50,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}UNION 高軌道空間站
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 你是Flag Fighter吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都不認識 你新來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是AEU的王牌 巴特裏克·戈拉索瓦大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈拉索瓦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.90,0:03:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.82,0:03:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 最先遭遇Gundam並一敗塗地那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別揭人傷疤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你們UNION的一把手在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾卡上級大尉不參加本次作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.12,0:03:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 怯場了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UNION的王牌也沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許誣蔑隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反 反對暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.39,0:03:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的部下失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是UNION的達利爾·達吉准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是AEU的卡蒂·瑪內金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負責指揮本次作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教  准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我將全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.40,0:03:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特裏克 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 上校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然會有戰果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則放棄Flag就毫無意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.44,0:04:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒臉見隊長了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾德也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是任務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統的構築情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概完成80%了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣做好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除了Veda對Gundam的輔助 機師的負擔會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不是酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:05:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近變得溫和多了 菲爾德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好傾向 好傾向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麻煩你們 再加把勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從目前情況看來 確實有人利用了Veda的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在沒有Veda的情況下對抗同型機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·史特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有Veda的輔助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有Gundam和Miss.皇的戰術預報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你還不知道 她過去曾犯下的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.92,0:05:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人都會犯錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也許犯下過天大的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但Miss.皇正是為了償還過去 才選擇了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能用酒撫慰痛苦的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過能做到這一點的 也只有人類而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 你知道我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位 皇小姐下令在集裝箱內待機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞 我就說一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為現在情勢不妙 四架Gundam的合作才更顯得重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話該去跟剎那·F·清英說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 這倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.94,0:07:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜·伊斯邁爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這邊來  索蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片土地上 也有了綻放的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽能發電能讓土地和人民都回歸這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 一定會變得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你不用再戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足夠了 索蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 會夢到瑪莉娜·伊斯邁爾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 問題在於 我想放棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想著要放棄嗎 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校 即將到達目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頂武GN-X部隊 開始對「天人」的設施進行攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再度品嚐勝利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.24,0:09:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被預測到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊墜一架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了High Mega才擊墜一架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被判我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一開始就打算拉我們陪葬嗎 拉格納·哈維
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.22,0:09:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總 總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne 合體解除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從敵方部隊中央突破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 謝謝你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.60,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}單體操作系統
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前E傳感器竟然都沒有反應 也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆都換上宇航服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 第一級戰鬥戰備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方部隊 斷定為擬太陽爐搭載型19架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19架…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方已捕捉到我方蹤跡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我們的專長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam四機從集裝箱緊急出動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.25,0:10:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以陣型S34迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方部隊接近至0130
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以為能出其不意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集裝箱艙門 打開
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機 陣型S34
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別大意喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:01.03,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}經濟特區 東京
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父親 曾是位自由新聞記者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新聞界裏 庫斯洛特這個名字無人不知
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的姐姐進入本報社
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是因為父親的影響吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.89,0:11:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因受到採訪對像公司的誣陷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判刑坐牢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去探監的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親經常這樣對姐姐說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探究事實
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順藤摸瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.17,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以絹江如此地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐在調查什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她不是交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她 是為了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絹江 她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在進行伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格的專題調查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？ 伊奧利亞…就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被認為是「天人」創立者的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 沙慈君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果當時我阻止她的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,視認Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.82,0:13:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預測到我們的行動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來有位優秀的指揮官啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相同性能的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模擬戰中不知失敗為何物的我更有優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿透了Field！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.24,0:13:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的粒子壓縮率被解讀了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只擦邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先行的兩架正接近Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 達利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到我們了 夥計們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.75,0:14:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有迴避點 沒有迴避點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我們的毀滅也是計劃中的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 Veda的輔助竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統出錯 系統出錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正要接受制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒過癮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.95,0:15:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被Veda拋棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的行動很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱嗎 還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全一樣 和當時…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明駕駛著Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻無法成為Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞厲桑德羅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:58.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了世界的統一 聯合國軍的勝利 這是必不可少的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要留下GN Drive 「天人」組織隨時可以東山再起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個慾望很強烈的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球與「天人」 兩樣都想得到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的系統死機 是Veda的介入
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照預定方案 變更為我們自己的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了嗎 我的 生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經足夠了 索蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活著  還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動起來 Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我動起來啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.37,0:16:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始運行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.53,0:17:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐 Virtue的系統更換出現錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 一定要趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人怕出名豬怕壯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我笑納了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.61,0:17:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校的熱吻到手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連本帶利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘餘的粒子不多了 上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認撤退信號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 上校的熱吻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這樣對不起隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.38,0:19:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames損傷 Dynames損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂負傷 洛克昂負傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 為了保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂·史特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同凡響啊 「天人」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然構築起了備用系統
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色的戰術預測
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是皇·李·諾列嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各機 回收Dynames和Virtue 動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲汀娜 聯繫莫雷諾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歷桑德羅大人 Level 6完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快了 就快…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為臨時編成的部隊 成果還算過得去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優先推進GN Drive的解析和量產化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 我們陣營也能與他們一較高下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備會談
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的時代結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界將因此而改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:55.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ笑顔してた　そんな僕らも　幾年も重ね過ぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:21:03.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違う景色を　受け入れられずに　もがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:11.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無駄なプライド捨て去り
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:16.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この世界に優しさを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:23.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}勇気を見せつけても　強がっても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:28.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一人では生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.79,0:21:32.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あの日の約束なら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:37.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の深くに残っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:42.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:48.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れちゃいけないから Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:53.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:22:00.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この広い大地と仲間達のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:55.09,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}經久不變的笑顏　是這樣的我們　在年輪中週而復始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:21:03.83,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}擦身而過的風景　卻無法剪下收藏　唯心房中絲縷焦急
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:11.09,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}將無謂的自尊遠遠拋棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:16.73,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用溫柔將這個世界抱緊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:18.13,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:23.41,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使告訴我你的勇氣　即使逞強
